msprocess_plots//preferred.out               ! output file name for focal mechanisms
msprocess_plots//acceptable.out              ! output file name for acceptable planes
.                           ! output file path for Early-est/GMT plot files
10                          ! minimum number of polarities (e.g., 8)
180                         ! maximum azimuthal gap (e.g., 90)
90                          ! maximum takeoff angle gap (e.g., 60)
2                           ! grid angle for focal mech search, in degrees         (min    5.0000000     )
1                           ! number of trials (e.g., 30)
500                         ! maxout for focal mech. output (e.g., 500)
0.1                         ! fraction of picks presumed bad (e.g., 0.10)
90                          ! maximum allowed source-station distance,                    in km (e.g., 120)
45                          ! angle for computing mechanisms probability,                 in degrees (e.g., 45)
0.25                        ! probability threshold for multiples (e.g., 0.1)

